  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Add the <strong>sweetcorn cobettes</strong> to a large piece of <strong>tin foil</strong> with<strong> half </strong>the <strong>smoked paprika </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Scrunch the <strong>tin foil</strong> around the corn until tightly sealed and add to the baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until the corn is tender – this is your <strong>smoky corn</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1669122298976-x200.jpg",
