    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse the<strong> black beans</strong></p><p>Dissolve the <strong>tomato paste </strong>and<strong> </strong>1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>in 75ml<strong> </strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
